{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales", "channel": "q2_sales", "user": "mgonzalez", "message": "Good morning team, let's aim to have the Q2 sales report finalized by the end of this week. Please ensure all your data is updated.", "created_at": 1620501000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales", "channel": "q2_sales", "user": "jdoe", "message": "Sure Maria, I'll have my section completed by tomorrow.", "created_at": 1620502000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "product", "channel": "kimchi_sales", "user": "jross", "message": "Team, we've received some interesting feedback on the kimchi packaging. I'll share the details in our next meeting.", "created_at": 1620503000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "product", "channel": "kimchi_sales", "user": "mgonzalez", "message": "Thanks Jennifer, looking forward to hearing more about it.", "created_at": 1620504000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales", "channel": "q2_sales", "user": "mgonzalez", "message": "Team, remember that our weekly sales meeting is moved to Thursday this week. Please adjust your schedules accordingly.", "created_at": 1620505000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "product", "channel": "kimchi_sales", "user": "jross", "message": "Can we have a brainstorming session next week to discuss potential improvements in our kimchi product line?", "created_at": 1620506000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales", "channel": "q2_sales", "user": "jdoe", "message": "Maria, I've scheduled a training session for the new sales software next Monday. I'll send out invites later today.", "created_at": 1620507000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "product", "channel": "kimchi_sales", "user": "mgonzalez", "message": "Great idea Jennifer. Let's schedule it for next Tuesday.", "created_at": 1620508000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales", "channel": "q2_sales", "user": "jdoe", "message": "Hey team, I'm just reviewing the sales data for Q2 2025. It looks like our decision to expand our Kimchi offerings in the New York City store has paid off.", "create_at": 1620500000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales", "channel": "q2_sales", "user": "mgonzalez", "message": "That's great news, John. Do we have any specifics on the revenue generated from Kimchi sales in the NYC store during Q2?", "create_at": 1620500000100}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales", "channel": "q2_sales", "user": "jdoe", "message": "Yes, Maria. The revenue generated by Lee's Market in Q2 2025 by selling Kimchi in its New York City store was approximately $120,000.", "create_at": 1620500000200}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "product", "channel": "kimchi_sales", "user": "jross", "message": "The increase in Kimchi sales in Q2 is encouraging. It's important to note that this is unrelated to the optimization of the bakery area layout of Lee's Market to increase bakery sales. We should continue to focus on individual product strategies for maximum effectiveness.", "create_at": 1620500000300}}
